headline: CHIPOTLE TEAMS UP WITH ELITE COLLEGE ATHLETIC PROGRAMS TO FUEL STUDENT ATHLETES WITH REAL FOOD
summary: Chipotle Mexican Grill (NYSE: CMG) today announced a partnership with all student athletes at The Ohio State University, University of Florida and University of Georgia, giving each of them access to free Chipotle during their respective athletic seasons.
